{
  "texts": [
    "however, lies in the processing and interpretation of the highdimensional data produced.",
    "Inputting a gene expression profile for a single cell from scRNA-seq, the cell type annotation task identifies the cell type from which the profile came from.",
    "Traditional cell type annotation methods rely on manual labeling of the unsupervised clustering results.",
    "This process requires the analysis of the expression results of specific marker genes.",
    "However, the available marker genes are limited and overlapping, especially for similar cell subtypes."
  ]
}